4. TARGET USERS & PERSONAS
================================================================================

Persona 1 — RL Researcher
    - Trains agents using PPO / DQN / custom algorithms.
    - Needs reproducible episodes (seed support), structured observations, and
      well-defined reward signals.

Persona 2 — AI Engineer
    - Integrates LLM-based agents (GPT, Claude, Gemini) with the environment.
    - Uses the REST / WebSocket API to build agentic pipelines.
    - Values clear action schemas and typed Pydantic models.

Persona 3 — Hackathon Participant
    - Needs a quick-start path: reset → step → grade.
    - Relies on the /baseline endpoint as a reference score.
    - Uses the Gradio /web UI for interactive exploration.

Persona 4 — Support Operations Lead
    - Evaluates whether an AI agent is ready for production.
    - Cares about escalation accuracy, response quality, and harmful-response
      detection.

